data.name: Ramus, the Supersonic
data.notes: "Ramus, the Supersonic" flies in one of groups of Aetrygon above the north east corner of Lake Ciel. Specifically in the group that flies near the level 60 Assault Launcher Zig that lies at the end of a deliberate footpath that climbs the small mountain that borders the north of Lake Ciel in Sylvalum.
